Test case:  Simple if with equals

If:
  object: a value
  equals: a value
  Do:
    ${result}: Match

Expected result: Match


---
Test case:  Simple if with 'in'

If:
  object: chocolate
  in:
  - milk
  - chocolate
  - cookies
  Do:
    ${chocolate}: Found

Assert that:
- object: ${chocolate}
  equals: Found


---
Test case:  If with and / or

If:
  all:
  - object: a value
    equals: a value
  - any:
    - object: selection
      equals: nothing
    - object: selection
      equals: selection
  Do:
    ${result}: Any Match

Expected result: Any Match


---
Test case:  If matching each item; no break

If:
- object: one
  equals: one
  Do:
    ${one}: 1
- object: two
  equals: two
  Do:
    ${two}: 2

Assert equals:
- actual:
  - ${one}
  - ${two}
  expected:
  - 1
  - 2


---
Test case: If then else; break after successful match

If any:
- object: a value
  equals: a value
  Do:
    ${first}: First match
- object: another value
  in: another value
  Do:
    ${second}: Second match
- ${default}: Deafult match

Assert equals:
- actual:
  - ${first}
  - ${second}
  - ${default}
  expected:
  - First match
  - ${second}
  - ${default}


---
Test case:  Variable resolution in nested Do

${result}: one

If:
  object: something
  equals: something
  Do:
  - ${result}: two
  - ${var}: ${result}

Assert equals:
- actual: ${var}
  expected: two


